# **Immediate Food Delivery**

**Difficulty:** Medium  •  **Tags:** 



## **Problem Description**

Solve the Immediate Food Delivery problem using SQL.



## **Table Schema**

**t36**
```
+--------+------+
| Column | Type |
+--------+------+
| id     | INT  |
| val    | INT  |
+--------+------+
```



## **Example**

### **Input**

**t36**
```
+----+-----+
| id | val |
+----+-----+
| 1  | 10  |
| 2  | 20  |
| 3  | 30  |
+----+-----+
```

### **Expected Output**

```
+----+-----+
| id | val |
+----+-----+
| 1  | 10  |
| 2  | 20  |
| 3  | 30  |
+----+-----+
```
